node.text: Glad to speak about life, hurt, the journey, love, and so much more. Shoutout to the @hoffmanprocess who I discussed here and thankful that I had the opportunity to give myself that gift of learning this year. I highly recommend the process to all. Thanks to Jay again for the important convo and we hope it helps.

node.text: Beyond proud of my friend @jonmchu for what he has done here with this film. #intheheights is a must watch this week. Best film of the year! I had the honor of growing up with two best friends @cuartas51 and his twin brother Fernando whose family was from Colombia. So many weekends I was brought in as the gringo who got to learn Salsa and  Merengue in their living room as their family filled the house with music and joy. Watching this film brought back so back many memories. I’m excited for everyone to feel the joy of the Latin culture and the music of Lin-Manuel Miranda. I have no business interest in this film. This long winded endorsement is just because it would bring me great joy knowing that others got to experience what I have already had the honor of experiencing. Watch this movie. Bravo to all involved.

node.title: I’m so excited for this movie

node.text: The new doc from Oscar nominated director @mheineman about @jbalvin is out now on Amazon Prime. #theboyfrommedellín . This is about so much more than music. Must watch film . And I hope when you are done you educate yourself on the current climate of the people of Colombia and use your own voice to help others. This film is incredibly moving. Congrats to all involved and happy birthday Jose.

node.text: Love you and Happy birthday @justinbieber . I have never shared this video before but I told you this week I would. As promised this is the very first time I ever heard you sing live. I had just picked you up from the airport (from your first flight ever... man how things have changed lol) and we went to my friends backyard and this happened. We have been through so much together since and I could not be prouder of the man , friend, husband, and leader you are today. So to celebrate you I have finally shared this one. Enjoy. Happy 27th birthday big man and love you for life. #day1 #happybirthdayjustin #family
OUT NOW🔥FUCK LOVE 3: OVER YOU ❤️‍🩹 @thekidlaroi 🚀 congrats young buck
